    <item>
      <title>日本新领导人正努力阻止选举失利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-10-22/japan-s-new-leader-ishiba-races-to-stem-electoral-bleeding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政党似乎将迎来一场激烈的选举之夜。其领导人石破茂面临的问题是损失会有多严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-10-22/japan-s-new-leader-ishiba-races-to-stem-electoral-bleeding</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 20:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFTC 负责人表示，选举押注和加密货币令该机构捉襟见肘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/cftc-chief-sees-agency-stretched-thin-by-election-bets-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国商品期货交易委员会主席罗斯汀·贝纳姆（Rostin Behnam）在接受彭博电视采访时表示，法院判决允许投机者押注选举结果的合约合法化后，美国商品期货交易委员会正处于“转折点”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/cftc-chief-sees-agency-stretched-thin-by-election-bets-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国林德纳称美国大选是对自由民主的投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-election-is-vote-on-liberal-democracy-germany-s-lindner-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，即将举行的美国大选结果不仅仅是一个国内问题，也是对全球自由民主和西方价值观的未来的投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-election-is-vote-on-liberal-democracy-germany-s-lindner-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:37:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦称与中国的债务重组谈判令人鼓舞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦财政部长表示，中国对巴基斯坦延长“一带一路”倡议相关债务期限的请求做出了令人鼓舞的回应，这意味着这个饱受过去高昂借贷压力的国家有了更多的喘息空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/pakistan-says-debt-reprofile-talks-with-china-are-encouraging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 19:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度取消部分大米出口税以提高竞争力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/india-scraps-tax-on-some-rice-exports-to-boost-competitiveness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度取消了对非巴斯马蒂蒸谷米出口的限制，此举可能增强该国在国际市场上的竞争力，并在当前收获季节提高当地农民的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/india-scraps-tax-on-some-rice-exports-to-boost-competitiveness</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯和内塔尼亚胡一致认为辛瓦尔之死为未来打开了选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/blinken-and-netanyahu-agree-sinwar-s-death-opens-possibilities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高外交官和以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡星期二一致认为，哈马斯领导人叶海亚辛瓦尔之死为结束加沙地带冲突开辟了新的可能性，但没有迹象表明这场持续两个半小时的会谈是否就下一步行动达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/blinken-and-netanyahu-agree-sinwar-s-death-opens-possibilities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦调查局调查以色列袭击计划机密文件泄露事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/fbi-probes-leak-of-top-secret-documents-on-israel-attack-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦调查局正在调查泄露的机密文件，该文件详细描述了以色列对伊朗采取报复行动的准备情况，美国官员试图严厉打击又一起令人尴尬的美国情报机密泄露事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/fbi-probes-leak-of-top-secret-documents-on-israel-attack-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 15:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦称美国将为乌克兰贷款提供 200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/yellen-says-us-aims-to-contribute-20-billion-for-ukraine-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特耶伦周二表示，美国几乎准备好向七国集团牵头的广泛贷款计划提供 200 亿美元来帮助乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/yellen-says-us-aims-to-contribute-20-billion-for-ukraine-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 15:11:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国认为俄罗斯、伊朗煽动选举后暴力事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/russia-iran-seen-by-us-as-instigators-of-violence-post-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国情报机构周二警告称，在 11 月 5 日大选后的几天和几周内，随着投票结果的统计和认证，俄罗斯和伊朗可能会试图在美国境内煽动暴力抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/russia-iran-seen-by-us-as-instigators-of-violence-post-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 15:07:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
